The First Selectman shall be the Chief Elected Officer of the Town. The First
Selectman shall be a voting and participating member of the Board of Selectmen
and shall preside at all meetings of said Board. The First Selectman or his/her
designee (who must be a Selectman) shall be an ex officio member of all other
town commissions, boards and agencies.